               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction&#xD;
- Mäqdǝmä wängel “Introduction to the Gospels” (fols. 1ra-4va; 6vb-14vb)&#xD;
- Stichometry (fols. 4va-4vb)&#xD;
- The “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 4vb-5va)&#xD;
- Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 5vb-6va)&#xD;
II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 13ra-49ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 66 titles (fols. 13ra-13vb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Matewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 14ra-49ra)&#xD;
III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 49ra-74va)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Mark: 47 titles (fols. 49ra-49va)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Marqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 50ra-74va)&#xD;
IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 74va-112ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 74 titles (fols. 72va-73va)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Luqas “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 74ra-112ra)&#xD;
V) Gospel of John (fols. 112ra-144ra)&#xD;
- List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 19 titles (fols. 112ra-112rb)&#xD;
- Bǝsratä Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 113ra-144ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
